oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall shaking hands with an unidentified United States Air Force soldier
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall (standing on left) shaking hands with an unidentified United States Air Force soldier. In the background, there are unidentified U.S. Air Force soldiers standing under a Boeing C-97 Stratofreighter. Image is an official U.S. Air Force Photograph taken at the Kelly Air Force Base in San Antonio, Texas.
